#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:44
msgid ""
"database:a range in which rows of related information are records and "
"columns of data are fields"
msgstr ""
"database:et interval hvor rækker af relateret information er poster og "
"kolonner af data er felter"

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:47
msgid "field:a string or integer specifying which field is to be used"
msgstr ""
"field:en tekststreng eller heltal der angiver hvilket felt der skal bruges"

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:49
msgid "criteria:a range containing conditions"
msgstr "criteria:et område der indeholder betingelser"

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:51
msgid ""
"@{database} is a range in which rows of related information are records and "
"columns of data are fields. The first row of a database contains labels for "
"each column."
msgstr ""
"@{database} er et interval hvor rækker af relateret information er poster og "
"kolonner af data er felter. Den første række i en database indeholder "
"etiketter for hver kolonne."

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:56
msgid ""
"@{field} is a string or integer specifying which field is to be used. If "
"@{field} is an integer n then the nth column will be used. If @{field} is a "
"string, then the column with the matching label will be used."
msgstr ""
"@{field} er en streng eller et heltal der angiver hvilket felt der skal "
"bruges. Hvis @{field} er et heltal n så vil den n'te kolonne blive brugt. "
"Hvis @{field} er en streng, så vil kolonnen med den tilsvarende etiket blive "
"brugt."

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:61
msgid ""
"@{criteria} is a range containing conditions. The first row of a @{criteria} "
"should contain labels. Each label specifies to which field the conditions "
"given in that column apply. Each cell below the label specifies a condition "
"such as \">3\" or \"<9\". An equality condition can be given by simply "
"specifying a value, e. g. \"3\" or \"Jody\". For a record to be considered "
"it must satisfy all conditions in at least one of the rows of @{criteria}."
msgstr ""
"@{criteria} er et interval der indeholder betingelser. Den første række i en "
"@{criteria} skal indeholde etiketter. Hver etiket angiver hvilket felt de "
"betingelser der er givet i den pågældende kolonne gælder for. Hver celle "
"under etiketten angiver en betingelse såsom \">3\" eller \"<9\". En "
"lighedsbetingelse kan gives ved blot at angive en værdi, f.eks. \"3\" eller "
"\"Jody\". For at en post skal blive betragtet skal den opfylde alle "
"betingelser i mindst én af rækkerne i @{criteria}."

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:72
msgid ""
"Let us assume that the range A1:C7 contain the following values:\n"
"\n"
"Name    \tAge     \tSalary\n"
"John    \t34      \t54342\n"
"Bill    \t35      \t22343\n"
"Clark   \t29      \t34323\n"
"Bob     \t43      \t47242\n"
"Susan   \t37      \t42932\n"
"Jill    \t\t45      \t45324\n"
"\n"
"In addition, the cells A9:B11 contain the following values:\n"
"Age     \tSalary\n"
"<30\n"
">40     \t>46000\n"
msgstr ""
"Lad os antage at intervallet A1:C7 indeholder følgende værdier:\n"
"\n"
"Navn    \tAlder     \tLøn\n"
"John    \t34      \t54342\n"
"Bill    \t35      \t22343\n"
"Clark   \t29      \t34323\n"
"Bob     \t43      \t47242\n"
"Susan   \t37      \t42932\n"
"Jill    \t\t45      \t45324\n"
"\n"
"Derudover indeholder cellerne A9:B11 følgende værdier:\n"
"Alder     \tLøn\n"
"<30\n"
">40     \t>46000\n"

