msgstr "field_name:navn på feltet som sammendragsdata ønskes for"

#: ../plugins/fn-database/functions.c:823
msgid "If the summary data is unavailable, GETPIVOTDATA returns #REF!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis sammendragsdataene ikke er tilgængelige, så returnerer GETPIVOTDATA "
"#REF!"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:72
msgid "DATE:create a date serial value"
msgstr "DATE:Lav et dagnummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:73
msgid "year:year of date"
msgstr "year:årstal"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:74
msgid "month:month of year"
msgstr "month:måned"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:75
msgid "day:day of month"
msgstr "day:dag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:76
msgid ""
"The DATE function creates date serial values.  1-Jan-1900 is serial value 1, "
"2-Jan-1900 is serial value 2, and so on.  For compatibility reasons, a "
"serial value is reserved for the non-existing date 29-Feb-1900."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen DATE opretter datoserieværdier. 1-jan-1900 er serieværdi 1, 2-"
"jan-1900 er serieværdi 2, og så videre. Af hensyn til kompatibilitet er en "
"serieværdi reserveret til den ikke-eksisterende dato 29-feb-1900."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:77
msgid ""
"If @{month} or @{day} is less than 1 or too big, then the year and/or month "
"will be adjusted."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{month} eller @{day} er mindre end 1 eller for stor, så vil året og/"
"eller måneden blive justeret."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:78
msgid ""
"For spreadsheets created with the Mac version of Excel, serial 1 is 1-"
"Jan-1904."
msgstr ""
"For regneark oprettet med Mac-versionen af Excel er serieværdi 1 lig med 1-"
"jan-1904."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:208
msgid "UNIX2DATE:date value corresponding to the Unix timestamp @{t}"
msgstr "UNIX2DATE:Datoværdi svarende til Unix-tidsstempel @{t}"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:209
msgid "t:Unix time stamp"
msgstr "t:Unix-tidsstempel"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:210
msgid ""
"The UNIX2DATE function translates Unix timestamps into the corresponding "
"date.  A Unix timestamp is the number of seconds since midnight (0:00) of "
"January 1st, 1970 GMT."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen UNIX2DATE oversætter Unix-tidsstempler til den tilsvarende dato. "
"Et Unix-tidsstempel er antallet af sekunder siden midnat (0:00) den 1. "
"januar 1970 GMT."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:238
msgid "DATE2UNIX:the Unix timestamp corresponding to a date @{d}"
msgstr "DATE2UNIX:Unix-tidsstempel svarende til dato @{d}"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:239
msgid "d:date"
msgstr "d:dato"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:240
msgid ""
"The DATE2UNIX function translates a date into a Unix timestamp. A Unix "
"timestamp is the number of seconds since midnight (0:00) of January 1st, "
"1970 GMT."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen DATE2UNIX oversætter en dato til et Unix-tidsstempel. Et Unix-"
"tidsstempel er antallet af sekunder siden midnat (0:00) den 1. januar 1970 "
"GMT."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:264
msgid "DATEVALUE:the date part of a date and time serial value"
msgstr "DATEVALUE:Datodelen af en dato- og tidsserial værdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:265 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:553
msgid "serial:date and time serial value"
msgstr "serial:dato- og tidsserieværdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:266
msgid ""
"DATEVALUE returns the date serial value part of a date and time serial value."
msgstr ""
"DATEVALUE returnerer datoserieværdidelen af en dato- og tidsserieværdi."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:282
msgid "DATEDIF:difference between dates"
msgstr "DATEDIF:Forskellen mellem datoer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:283 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:783
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1100 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1283
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1441 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1471
msgid "start_date:starting date serial value"
msgstr "start_date:startdatoens serieværdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:284 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:784
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1101 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1284
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1442 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1470
msgid "end_date:ending date serial value"
msgstr "end_date:slutdatoens serieværdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:285
msgid "interval:counting unit"
msgstr "interval:tælleenhed"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:286
msgid ""
"DATEDIF returns the distance from @{start_date} to @{end_date} according to "
"the unit specified by @{interval}.  This function exists primarly for "
"compatibility reasons and the semantics is somewhat peculiar.  In "
"particular, the concept of \"whole month\" is based on whether the ending "
"day is larger than or equal to the beginning day and not on whether a whole "
"calendar month in contained in the interval.  A similar treatment is given "
"to \"whole year\"."
msgstr ""
"DATEDIF returnerer afstanden fra @{start_date} til @{end_date} i henhold til "
"den enhed, der er angivet ved @{interval}. Denne funktion findes primært af "
"hensyn til kompatibilitet, og semantikken er en smule ejendommelig. Navnlig "
"er begrebet \"hel måned\" baseret på, om slutdagen er større end eller lig "
"med startdagen, og ikke på om en hel kalendermåned er indeholdt i "
"intervallet. En lignende behandling gives til \"helt år\"."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:287
msgid ""
"If @{interval} is \"y\", \"m\", or \"d\" then the distance is measured in "
"whole years, months, or days respectively."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{interval} er \"y\", \"m\" eller \"d\", måles afstanden i henholdsvis "
"hele år, måneder eller dage."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:288
msgid ""
"If @{interval} is \"ym\" or \"yd\" then the distance is measured in whole "
"months or days, respectively, but excluding any difference covered by whole "
"years."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{interval} er \"ym\" eller \"yd\", måles afstanden i henholdsvis hele "
"måneder eller dage, men eksklusive forskelle dækket af hele år."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:289
msgid ""
"If @{interval} is \"md\" then the distance is measured in days but excluding "
"any difference covered by whole months."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{interval} er \"md\", måles afstanden i dage, men eksklusive forskelle "
"dækket af hele måneder."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:418
msgid "EDATE:adjust a date by a number of months"
msgstr "EDATE:Juster en dato med et antal måneder"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:419 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:641
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:665 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:689
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:713 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:825
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:865 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1049
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1311 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1335
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1371
msgid "date:date serial value"
msgstr "date:datoserieværdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:420 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:826
msgid "months:signed number of months"
msgstr "months:antal måneder med fortegn"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:421
msgid ""
"EDATE returns @{date} moved forward or backward the number of months "
"specified by @{months}."
msgstr ""
"EDATE returnerer @{date} flyttet frem eller tilbage med det antal måneder, "
"der er angivet i @{months}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:455
msgid "TODAY:the date serial value of today"
msgstr "TODAY:Dags datos dagnummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:456
msgid ""
"The TODAY function returns the date serial value of the day it is computed.  "
"Recomputing on a later date will produce a different value."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen TODAY returnerer datoserieværdien for den dag, den beregnes. "
"Genberegning på en senere dato vil give en anden værdi."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:472
msgid "NOW:the date and time serial value of the current time"
msgstr "NOW:Dato- og tidsserial værdi for det nuværende tidspunkt"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:473
msgid ""
"The NOW function returns the date and time serial value of the moment it is "
"computed.  Recomputing later will produce a different value."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen NOW returnerer dato- og tidsserieværdien for det øjeblik, den "
"beregnes. Genberegning senere vil give en anden værdi."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:492
msgid "TIME:create a time serial value"
msgstr "TIME:Opret en tidsserial værdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:493
msgid "hour:hour of the day"
msgstr "hour:time på dagen"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:494
msgid "minute:minute within the hour"
msgstr "minute:minut i timen"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:495
msgid "second:second within the minute"
msgstr "second:sekund i minuttet"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:496
msgid ""
"The TIME function computes the fractional day after midnight at the time "
"given by @{hour}, @{minute}, and @{second}."
msgstr ""
"TIME-funktionen beregner brøkdelen af dagen efter midnat på det tidspunkt "
"givet ved @{hour}, @{minute} og @{second}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:497
msgid ""
"While the return value is automatically formatted to look like a time "
"between 0:00 and 24:00, the underlying serial time value is a number between "
"0 and 1."
msgstr ""
"Selvom returværdien automatisk formateres til at ligne et tidspunkt mellem "
"0:00 og 24:00, er den underliggende serie-tidsværdi et tal mellem 0 og 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:499
msgid ""
"If the total time is negative, the result is the time wrapped around "
"midnight."
msgstr ""
"Hvis den samlede tid er negativ, er resultatet tiden foldet omkring midnat."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:524
msgid "ODF.TIME:create a time serial value"
msgstr "ODF.TIME:Opret en tidsserial værdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:525
msgid "hour:hour"
msgstr "hour:time"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:526
msgid "minute:minute"
msgstr "minute:minut"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:527
msgid "second:second"
msgstr "second:sekund"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:528
msgid ""
"The ODF.TIME function computes the time given by @{hour}, @{minute}, and "
"@{second} as a fraction of a day."
msgstr ""
"ODF.TIME-funktionen beregner tidspunktet givet ved @{hour}, @{minute} og "
"@{second} som en brøkdel af en dag."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:529
msgid ""
"While the return value is automatically formatted to look like a time "
"between 0:00 and 24:00, the underlying serial time value can be any number."
msgstr ""
"Selvom returværdien automatisk formateres til at ligne et tidspunkt mellem "
"0:00 og 24:00, kan den underliggende serie-tidsværdi være et hvilket som "
"helst tal."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:533 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:874
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1109 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1473
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:221 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:325
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:395 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:842
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:1251 ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:575
#: ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:1181 ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:1208
#: ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:1674 ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:1694
#: ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:2573 ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:3237
#: ../plugins/fn-math/functions.c:3436 ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:1761
#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:2707 ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:5064
#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:353 ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:440
#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:567 ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:1565
#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:2173 ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:2422
msgid "This function is OpenFormula compatible."
msgstr "Denne funktion er OpenFormula-kompatibel."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:552
msgid "TIMEVALUE:the time part of a date and time serial value"
msgstr "TIMEVALUE:Tidsdelen af en dato- og tidsserial værdi"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:554
msgid "TIMEVALUE returns the time-of-day part of a date and time serial value."
msgstr ""
"TIMEVALUE returnerer tidspunktet på dagen-delen af en dato- og "
"tidsserieværdi."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:571
msgid "HOUR:compute hour part of fractional day"
msgstr "HOUR:Beregn timedel af brøkdel af dag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:572 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:595
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:618
msgid "time:time of day as fractional day"
msgstr "time:tidspunkt på dagen som brøkdel af dag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:573
msgid ""
"The HOUR function computes the hour part of the fractional day given by "
"@{time}."
msgstr ""
"HOUR-funktionen beregner time-delen af den brøkdel af dagen givet ved "
"@{time}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:594
msgid "MINUTE:compute minute part of fractional day"
msgstr "MINUTE:Beregn minutdel af brøkdel af dag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:596
msgid ""
"The MINUTE function computes the minute part of the fractional day given by "
"@{time}."
msgstr ""
"MINUTE-funktionen beregner minut-delen af den brøkdel af dagen givet ved "
"@{time}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:617
msgid "SECOND:compute seconds part of fractional day"
msgstr "SECOND:Beregn sekunddel af brøkdel af dag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:619
msgid ""
"The SECOND function computes the seconds part of the fractional day given by "
"@{time}."
msgstr ""
"SECOND-funktionen beregner sekund-delen af den brøkdel af dagen givet ved "
"@{time}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:640
msgid "YEAR:the year part of a date serial value"
msgstr "YEAR:årsdelen af et dagnummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:642
msgid "The YEAR function returns the year part of @{date}."
msgstr "YEAR-funktionen returnerer årsdelen af @{date}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:664
msgid "MONTH:the month part of a date serial value"
msgstr "MONTH:Månedsdelen af et dagnummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:666
msgid "The MONTH function returns the month part of @{date}."
msgstr "MONTH-funktionen returnerer månedsdelen af @{date}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:688
msgid "DAY:the day-of-month part of a date serial value"
msgstr "DAY:Dag-i-måned-delen af et dagnummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:690
msgid "The DAY function returns the day-of-month part of @{date}."
msgstr "DAY-funktionen returnerer dag-i-måneden-delen af @{date}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:712
msgid "WEEKDAY:day-of-week"
msgstr "WEEKDAY:Ugedag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:714 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1372
msgid "method:numbering system, defaults to 1"
msgstr "method:nummereringssystem, standardværdi er 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:715
msgid ""
"The WEEKDAY function returns the day-of-week of @{date}.  The value of "
"@{method} determines how days are numbered; it defaults to 1."
msgstr ""
"WEEKDAY-funktionen returnerer ugedagen for @{date}. Værdien af @{method} "
"bestemmer hvordan dage nummereres; standardværdien er 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:716
msgid "If @{method} is 1, then Sunday is 1, Monday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 1, er søndag 1, mandag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:717
msgid "If @{method} is 2, then Monday is 1, Tuesday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 2, er mandag 1, tirsdag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:718
msgid "If @{method} is 3, then Monday is 0, Tuesday is 1, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 3, er mandag 0, tirsdag 1 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:719
msgid "If @{method} is 11, then Monday is 1, Tuesday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 11, er mandag 1, tirsdag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:720
msgid "If @{method} is 12, then Tuesday is 1, Wednesday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 12, er tirsdag 1, onsdag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:721
msgid "If @{method} is 13, then Wednesday is 1, Thursday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 13, er onsdag 1, torsdag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:722
msgid "If @{method} is 14, then Thursday is 1, Friday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 14, er torsdag 1, fredag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:723
msgid "If @{method} is 15, then Friday is 1, Saturday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 15, er fredag 1, lørdag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:724
msgid "If @{method} is 16, then Saturday is 1, Sunday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 16, er lørdag 1, søndag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:725
msgid "If @{method} is 17, then Sunday is 1, Monday is 2, etc."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 17, er søndag 1, mandag 2 osv."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:782
msgid "DAYS360:days between dates"
msgstr "DAYS360:Dage mellem datoer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:785
msgid "method:counting method"
msgstr "method:tællemetode"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:786
msgid "DAYS360 returns the number of days from @{start_date} to @{end_date}."
msgstr "DAYS360 returnerer antallet af dage fra @{start_date} til @{end_date}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:787
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 0, the default, the MS Excel (tm) US method will be used. "
"This is a somewhat complicated industry standard method where the last day "
"of February is considered to be the 30th day of the month, but only for "
"@{start_date}."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 0, standardværdien, vil MS Excel (tm) US-metoden blive "
"brugt. Dette er en noget kompliceret industristandard-metode hvor den sidste "
"dag i februar betragtes som den 30. dag i måneden, men kun for @{start_date}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:788
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 1, the European method will be used.  In this case, if the "
"day of the month is 31 it will be considered as 30"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 1, vil den europæiske metode blive brugt. I dette "
"tilfælde, hvis dagen i måneden er 31 vil den blive betragtet som 30"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:789
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 2, a saner version of the US method is used in which both "
"dates get the same February treatment."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 2, bruges en mere fornuftig version af US-metoden hvor "
"begge datoer får samme februarbehandling."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:824
msgid "EOMONTH:end of month"
msgstr "EOMONTH:Slutningen af måneden"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:827
msgid ""
"EOMONTH returns the date serial value of the end of the month specified by "
"@{date} adjusted forward or backward the number of months specified by "
"@{months}."
msgstr ""
"EOMONTH returnerer dato-serieværdien for slutningen af den måned angivet af "
"@{date} justeret frem eller tilbage det antal måneder angivet af @{months}."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:864
msgid "WORKDAY:add working days"
msgstr "WORKDAY:Gå et antal arbejdsdage fremad"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:866 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1050
msgid "days:number of days to add"
msgstr "days:Antal dage der skal tilføjes"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:867 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1052
#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1102 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1286
msgid "holidays:array of holidays"
msgstr "holidays:Matrix af helligdage"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:868 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1103
msgid ""
"weekend:array of 0s and 1s, indicating whether a weekday (S, M, T, W, T, F, "
"S) is on the weekend, defaults to {1,0,0,0,0,0,1}"
msgstr ""
"weekend:Matrix af 0'er og 1'er, der indikerer hvorvidt en ugedag (S, M, T, "
"O, T, F, L) er weekend, standard er {1,0,0,0,0,0,1}"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:870
msgid ""
"WORKDAY adjusts @{date} by @{days} skipping over weekends and @{holidays} in "
"the process."
msgstr ""
"WORKDAY justerer @{date} med @{days} og springer over weekender og "
"@{holidays} i processen."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:871
msgid "@{days} may be negative."
msgstr "@{days} kan være negativ."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:872 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1107
msgid ""
"If an entry of @{weekend} is non-zero, the corresponding weekday is not a "
"work day."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en post i @{weekend} er ikke-nul, er den tilsvarende ugedag ikke en "
"arbejdsdag."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:873 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1108
msgid "This function is Excel compatible if the last argument is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Denne funktion er kompatibel med Excel hvis det sidste argument udelades."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1048
msgid "WORKDAY.INTL:add working days"
msgstr "WORKDAY.INTL:Gå et antal arbejdsdage fremad"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1051 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1285
msgid ""
"weekend:predefined weekend pattern (1-17) or 7-character string, defaults to "
"1"
msgstr ""
"weekend:foruddefineret weekendmønster (1-17) eller en streng på 7 tegn; "
"standard er 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1053
msgid ""
"WORKDAY.INTL adjusts @{date} by @{days} skipping over weekends and "
"@{holidays} in the process."
msgstr ""
"WORKDAY.INTL justerer @{date} med @{days} og springer over weekender og "
"@{holidays} i processen."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1099
msgid "NETWORKDAYS:number of workdays in range"
msgstr "NETWORKDAYS:Antal arbejdsdage i interval"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1105
msgid ""
"NETWORKDAYS calculates the number of days from @{start_date} to @{end_date} "
"skipping weekends and @{holidays} in the process."
msgstr ""
"NETWORKDAYS beregner antallet af dage fra @{start_date} til @{end_date} hvor "
"weekender og @{holidays} springes over i processen."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1282
msgid "NETWORKDAYS.INTL:number of workdays in range"
msgstr "NETWORKDAYS.INTL:antal arbejdsdage i interval"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1287
msgid ""
"NETWORKDAYS.INTL calculates the number of days from @{start_date} to "
"@{end_date} skipping weekends and @{holidays} in the process."
msgstr ""
"NETWORKDAYS.INTL beregner antallet af dage fra @{start_date} til @{end_date} "
"hvor weekender og @{holidays} springes over i processen."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1310
msgid "ISOWEEKNUM:ISO week number"
msgstr "ISOWEEKNUM:ISO-ugenummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1312
msgid ""
"ISOWEEKNUM calculates the week number according to the ISO 8601 standard.  "
"Weeks start on Mondays and week 1 contains the first Thursday of the year."
msgstr ""
"ISOWEEKNUM beregner ugenummeret i henhold til ISO 8601-standarden. Uger "
"starter om mandagen og uge 1 indeholder årets første torsdag."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1313 ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1337
msgid ""
"January 1 of a year is sometimes in week 52 or 53 of the previous year.  "
"Similarly, December 31 is sometimes in week 1 of the following year."
msgstr ""
"1. januar i et år er sommetider i uge 52 eller 53 af det foregående år. "
"Tilsvarende er 31. december sommetider i uge 1 af det følgende år."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1334
msgid "ISOYEAR:year corresponding to the ISO week number"
msgstr "ISOYEAR:år svarende til ISO-ugenummeret"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1336
msgid ""
"ISOYEAR calculates the year to go with week number according to the ISO 8601 "
"standard."
msgstr ""
"ISOYEAR beregner året der hører til ugenummeret i henhold til ISO 8601-"
"standarden."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1370
msgid "WEEKNUM:week number"
msgstr "WEEKNUM:Ugenummer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1373
msgid ""
"WEEKNUM calculates the week number according to @{method} which defaults to "
"1."
msgstr ""
"WEEKNUM beregner ugenummeret i henhold til @{method} som har standardværdien "
"1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1374
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 1, then weeks start on Sundays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 1, så starter en uge på en søndag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1375
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 2, then weeks start on Mondays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 2, så starter en uge på en mandag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1376
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 11, then weeks start on Mondays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 11, så starter en uge på en mandag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1377
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 12, then weeks start on Tuesdays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 12, så starter en uge på en tirsdag og 1. januar er i uge "
"1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1378
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 13, then weeks start on Wednesdays and January 1 is in week "
"1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 13, så starter en uge på en onsdag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1379
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 14, then weeks start on Thursdays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 14, så starter en uge på en torsdag og 1. januar er i uge "
"1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1380
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 15, then weeks start on Fridays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 15, så starter en uge på en fredag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1381
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 16, then weeks start on Saturdays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 16, så starter en uge på en lørdag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1382
msgid ""
"If @{method} is 17, then weeks start on Sundays and January 1 is in week 1."
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{method} er 17, så starter en uge på en søndag og 1. januar er i uge 1."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1383
msgid "If @{method} is 21 or 150, then the ISO 8601 numbering is used."
msgstr "Hvis @{method} er 21 eller 150, så bruges ISO 8601-nummerering."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1440
msgid "YEARFRAC:fractional number of years between dates"
msgstr "YEARFRAC:Antal år som brøkdel mellem datoer"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1443 ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:451
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:485
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:518
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:554
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:586
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:625
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:1835
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2194
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2244
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2351
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2392
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2430
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2581
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2676
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2754
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2831
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2883
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2922
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2946
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2970
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:2994
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:3020
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:3046
#: ../plugins/fn-financial/functions.c:3154
msgid "basis:calendar basis"
msgstr "basis:kalendergrundlag"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1444
msgid ""
"YEARFRAC calculates the number of days from @{start_date} to @{end_date} "
"according to the calendar specified by @{basis}, which defaults to 0, and "
"expresses the result as a fractional number of years."
msgstr ""
"YEARFRAC beregner antallet af dage fra @{start_date} til @{end_date} i "
"henhold til kalenderen angivet af @{basis}, som har standardværdien 0, og "
"udtrykker resultatet som et brøktal af år."

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1469
msgid "DAYS:difference between dates in days"
msgstr "DAYS:Forskellen mellem datoer i dage"

#: ../plugins/fn-date/functions.c:1472
msgid ""
"DAYS returns the positive or negative number of days from @{start_date} to "
"@{end_date}."
msgstr ""
"DAYS returnerer det positive eller negative antal dage fra @{start_date} til "
"@{end_date}."

#. Some common decriptors
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:44
msgid "call_put_flag:'c' for a call and 'p' for a put"
msgstr "call_put_flag:'c' for call og 'p' for put"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:45
msgid "spot:spot price"
msgstr "spot:spotpris"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:46
msgid "strike:strike price"
msgstr "strike:strike-pris"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:47
msgid "time:time to maturity in years"
msgstr "time:tid til udløb i år"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:48
msgid "time:time to maturity in days"
msgstr "time:tid til udløb i dage"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:49
msgid "time_payout:time to dividend payout"
msgstr "time_payout:tid til udbytteudbetaling"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:50
msgid "time_exp:time to expiration"
msgstr "time_exp:tid til udløb"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:51
msgid "rate:risk-free interest rate to the exercise date in percent"
msgstr "rate:risikofri rente til udnyttelsesdato i procent"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:52
msgid "rate:annualized interest rate"
msgstr "rate:årlig rente"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:53
msgid "rate:annualized risk-free interest rate"
msgstr "rate:årlig risikofri rente"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:54
msgid ""
"volatility:annualized volatility of the asset in percent for the period "
"through to the exercise date"
msgstr ""
"volatility:årlig volatilitet af aktivet i procent for perioden frem til "
"udnyttelsesdatoen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:55
msgid "volatility:annualized volatility of the asset"
msgstr "volatility:årlig volatilitet for aktivet"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:56
msgid "d:amount of the dividend to be paid expressed in currency"
msgstr "d:størrelse af det udbytte der skal betales udtrykt i valuta"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:57
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry:net cost of holding the underlying asset (for common stocks, "
"the risk free rate less the dividend yield), defaults to 0"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry:nettoomkostning ved at besidde det underliggende aktiv (for "
"almindelige aktier, den risikofrie rente minus udbytteudbyttet), "
"standardværdi er 0"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:58
msgid "cost_of_carry:net cost of holding the underlying asset"
msgstr "cost_of_carry:nettoomkostning ved at holde det underliggende aktiv"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:60
msgid ""
"The returned value will be expressed in the same units as @{strike} and "
"@{spot}."
msgstr ""
"Den returnerede værdi vil blive udtrykt i samme enheder som @{strike} og "
"@{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:190
msgid "CUM_BIV_NORM_DIST:cumulative bivariate normal distribution"
msgstr "CUM_BIV_NORM_DIST:Kumuleret bivariat normalfordeling"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:191
msgid "a:limit for first random variable"
msgstr "a:grænse for første stokastiske variabel"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:192
msgid "b:limit for second random variable"
msgstr "b:grænse for anden stokastiske variabel"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:193
msgid "rho:correlation of the two random variables"
msgstr "rho:korrelation mellem de to stokastiske variable"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:194
msgid ""
"CUM_BIV_NORM_DIST calculates the probability that two standard normal "
"distributed random variables with correlation @{rho} are respectively each "
"less than @{a} and @{b}."
msgstr ""
"CUM_BIV_NORM_DIST beregner sandsynligheden for at to standard normalfordelte "
"tilfældige variable med korrelation @{rho} hver især er mindre end "
"henholdsvis @{a} og @{b}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:243
msgid "OPT_BS:price of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS:Pris på en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:251
msgid ""
"OPT_BS uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the price of a European "
"option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne prisen på en europæisk "
"option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:300
msgid "OPT_BS_DELTA:delta of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_DELTA:Delta for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:308
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_DELTA uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'delta' of a "
"European option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_DELTA bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne 'delta' for en "
"europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:342
msgid "OPT_BS_GAMMA:gamma of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_GAMMA:Gamma for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:349
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_GAMMA uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'gamma' of a "
"European option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}. The "
"gamma of an option is the second derivative of its price with respect to the "
"price of the underlying asset."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_GAMMA bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne 'gamma' for en "
"europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}. "
"Gamma for en option er den anden afledte af dens pris med hensyn til prisen "
"på det underliggende aktiv."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:354
msgid ""
"Gamma is expressed as the rate of change of delta per unit change in @{spot}."
msgstr ""
"Gamma udtrykkes som ændringsraten af delta per enhedsændring i @{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:356
msgid "Gamma is the same for calls and puts."
msgstr "Gamma er det samme for calls og puts."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:399
msgid "OPT_BS_THETA:theta of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_THETA:Theta for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:407
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_THETA uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'theta' of a "
"European option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}. The "
"theta of an option is the rate of change of its price with respect to time "
"to expiry."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_THETA bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne 'theta' for en "
"europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}. "
"Theta for en option er ændringsraten af dens pris med hensyn til tid til "
"udløb."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:412
msgid ""
"Theta is expressed as the negative of the rate of change of the option "
"value, per 365.25 days."
msgstr ""
"Theta udtrykkes som det negative af ændringsraten af optionsværdien, per "
"365,25 dage."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:443
msgid "OPT_BS_VEGA:vega of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_VEGA:Vega for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:450
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_VEGA uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'vega' of a "
"European option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}. The "
"vega of an option is the rate of change of its price with respect to "
"volatility."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_VEGA bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne 'vega' for en "
"europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}. "
"Vega for en option er ændringsraten af dens pris med hensyn til volatilitet."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:455
msgid "Vega is the same for calls and puts."
msgstr "Vega er det samme for calls og puts."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Vega is expressed as the rate of change of option value, per 100% volatility."
msgstr ""
"Vega udtrykkes som ændringsraten af optionsværdien, per 100% volatilitet."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:508
msgid "OPT_BS_RHO:rho of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_RHO:Rho for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:516
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_RHO uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'rho' of a European "
"option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}. The rho of "
"an option is the rate of change of its price with respect to the risk free "
"interest rate."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_RHO bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne 'rho' for en "
"europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}. "
"Rho for en option er ændringsraten af dens pris med hensyn til den "
"risikofrie rente."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rho is expressed as the rate of change of the option value, per 100% change "
"in @{rate}."
msgstr ""
"Rho udtrykkes som ændringsraten af optionsværdien, per 100% ændring i "
"@{rate}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:564
msgid "OPT_BS_CARRYCOST:elasticity of a European option"
msgstr "OPT_BS_CARRYCOST:Elasticitet for en europæisk option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:572
msgid ""
"OPT_BS_CARRYCOST uses the Black-Scholes model to calculate the 'elasticity' "
"of a European option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price "
"@{spot}. The elasticity of an option is the rate of change of its price with "
"respect to its @{cost_of_carry}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_BS_CARRYCOST bruger Black-Scholes-modellen til at beregne "
"'elasticiteten' af en europæisk option med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv "
"med spotpris @{spot}. Elasticiteten af en option er ændringsraten af dens "
"pris med hensyn til dens @{cost_of_carry}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Elasticity is expressed as the rate of change of the option value, per 100% "
"volatility."
msgstr ""
"Elasticitet udtrykkes som ændringsraten af optionsværdien, per 100% "
"volatilitet."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:622
msgid "OPT_GARMAN_KOHLHAGEN:theoretical price of a European currency option"
msgstr "OPT_GARMAN_KOHLHAGEN:Teoretisk pris på en europæisk valutaoption"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:626
msgid "time:number of days to exercise"
msgstr "time:antal dage til udnyttelse"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:627
msgid ""
"domestic_rate:domestic risk-free interest rate to the exercise date in "
"percent"
msgstr ""
"domestic_rate:indenlandsk risikofri rente til udnyttelsesdatoen i procent"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:628
msgid ""
"foreign_rate:foreign risk-free interest rate to the exercise date in percent"
msgstr ""
"foreign_rate:udenlandsk risikofri rente til udnyttelsesdatoen i procent"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:630
msgid ""
"OPT_GARMAN_KOHLHAGEN values the theoretical price of a European currency "
"option struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price @{spot}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_GARMAN_KOHLHAGEN værdiansætter den teoretiske pris for en europæisk "
"valutaoption med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv med spotpris @{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:676
msgid ""
"OPT_FRENCH:theoretical price of a European option adjusted for trading day "
"volatility"
msgstr ""
"OPT_FRENCH:Teoretisk pris på en europæisk option justeret for "
"handelsdagsvolatilitet"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:680
msgid ""
"time:ratio of the number of calendar days to exercise and the number of "
"calendar days in the year"
msgstr ""
"time:forholdet mellem antallet af kalenderdage til udnyttelse og antallet af "
"kalenderdage i året"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:681
msgid ""
"ttime:ratio of the number of trading days to exercise and the number of "
"trading days in the year"
msgstr ""
"ttime:forholdet mellem antallet af handelsdage til udnyttelse og antallet af "
"handelsdage i året"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:685
msgid ""
"OPT_FRENCH values the theoretical price of a European option adjusted for "
"trading day volatility, struck at @{strike} on an asset with spot price "
"@{spot}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_FRENCH værdiansætter den teoretiske pris for en europæisk option "
"justeret for handelsdags-volatilitet, med strike-pris @{strike} på et aktiv "
"med spotpris @{spot}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:729
msgid ""
"OPT_JUMP_DIFF:theoretical price of an option according to the Jump Diffusion "
"process"
msgstr ""
"OPT_JUMP_DIFF:Teoretisk pris på en option ifølge jump-diffusion-processen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:734
msgid "rate:the annualized rate of interest"
msgstr "rate:den årlige rente"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:736
msgid "lambda:expected number of 'jumps' per year"
msgstr "lambda:forventet antal 'hop' per år"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:737
msgid "gamma:proportion of volatility explained by the 'jumps'"
msgstr "gamma:andel af volatilitet forklaret af 'hop'"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:738
msgid ""
"OPT_JUMP_DIFF models the theoretical price of an option according to the "
"Jump Diffusion process (Merton)."
msgstr ""
"OPT_JUMP_DIFF modellerer den teoretiske pris for en option i henhold til "
"Jump Diffusion-processen (Merton)."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:816
msgid ""
"OPT_MILTERSEN_SCHWARTZ:theoretical price of options on commodities futures "
"according to Miltersen & Schwartz"
msgstr ""
"OPT_MILTERSEN_SCHWARTZ:Teoretisk pris på optioner på råvarefutures ifølge "
"Miltersen & Schwartz"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:818
msgid "p_t:zero coupon bond with expiry at option maturity"
msgstr "p_t:nulkuponobligation med udløb ved optionens udløbstid"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:819
msgid "f_t:futures price"
msgstr "f_t:futurespris"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:821
msgid "t1:time to maturity of the option"
msgstr "t1:tid til optionens udløb"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:822
msgid "t2:time to maturity of the underlying commodity futures contract"
msgstr "t2:tid til udløb af den underliggende råvarefutureskontrakt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:823
msgid "v_s:volatility of the spot commodity price"
msgstr "v_s:volatilitet for spot-råvareprisen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:824
msgid "v_e:volatility of the future convenience yield"
msgstr "v_e:volatilitet for det fremtidige bekvemmelighedsudbytte"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:825
msgid "v_f:volatility of the forward rate of interest"
msgstr "v_f:volatilitet for terminrenten"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:826
msgid ""
"rho_se:correlation between the spot commodity price and the convenience yield"
msgstr "rho_se:korrelation mellem spotvareprisen og bekvemlighedsudbyttet"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:827
msgid ""
"rho_sf:correlation between the spot commodity price and the forward interest "
"rate"
msgstr "rho_sf:korrelation mellem spotvareprisen og terminsrenten"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:828
msgid ""
"rho_ef:correlation between the forward interest rate and the convenience "
"yield"
msgstr "rho_ef:korrelation mellem terminsrenten og bekvemlighedsudbyttet"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:829
msgid "kappa_e:speed of mean reversion of the convenience yield"
msgstr ""
"kappa_e:hastighed for middelværdi-tilbagevenden for bekvemmelighedsudbyttet"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:830
msgid "kappa_f:speed of mean reversion of the forward interest rate"
msgstr "kappa_f:hastighed for middelværdi-tilbagevenden for terminrenten"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:913
msgid ""
"OPT_RGW:theoretical price of an American option according to the Roll-Geske-"
"Whaley approximation"
msgstr ""
"OPT_RGW:Teoretisk pris på en amerikansk option ifølge Roll-Geske-Whaley-"
"approksimationen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:956
msgid ""
"OPT_BAW_AMER:theoretical price of an option according to the Barone Adesie & "
"Whaley approximation"
msgstr ""
"OPT_BAW_AMER:Teoretisk pris på en option ifølge Barone Adesie & Whaley-"
"approksimationen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1128
msgid ""
"OPT_BJER_STENS:theoretical price of American options according to the "
"Bjerksund & Stensland approximation technique"
msgstr ""
"OPT_BJER_STENS:Teoretisk pris for amerikanske optioner i henhold til "
"Bjerksund & Stensland-tilnærmelsesteknikken"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1202
msgid "OPT_EXEC:theoretical price of executive stock options"
msgstr "OPT_EXEC:Teoretisk pris på direktionsaktieoptioner"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1210
msgid "lambda:jump rate for executives"
msgstr "lambda:spring-rate for direktører"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1211
msgid ""
"The model assumes executives forfeit their options if they leave the company."
msgstr ""
"Modellen antager at ledere fortaber deres optioner hvis de forlader "
"virksomheden."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1238
msgid "OPT_FORWARD_START:theoretical price of forward start options"
msgstr "OPT_FORWARD_START:Teoretisk pris på fremadstartoptioner"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1241
msgid ""
"alpha:fraction setting the strike price at the future date @{time_start}"
msgstr ""
"alpha:brøkdel der fastsætter strike-prisen på den fremtidige dato "
"@{time_start}"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1242
msgid "time_start:time until the option starts in days"
msgstr "time_start:tid indtil optionen starter i dage"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1290
msgid "OPT_TIME_SWITCH:theoretical price of time switch options"
msgstr "OPT_TIME_SWITCH:Teoretisk pris på tidsskifteoptioner"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1294
msgid "a:amount received for each time period"
msgstr "a:beløb modtaget for hver tidsperiode"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1296
msgid "m:number of time units the option has already met the condition"
msgstr "m:antal tidsenheder optionen allerede har opfyldt betingelsen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1297
msgid "dt:agreed upon discrete time period expressed as a fraction of a year"
msgstr "dt:aftalt diskret tidsperiode udtrykt som brøkdel af et år"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1302
msgid ""
"OPT_TIME_SWITCH models the theoretical price of time switch options. (Pechtl "
"1995). The holder receives @{a} * @{dt} for each period that the asset price "
"was greater than @{strike} (for a call) or below it (for a put)."
msgstr ""
"OPT_TIME_SWITCH modellerer den teoretiske pris for time switch-optioner. "
"(Pechtl 1995). Indehaveren modtager @{a} * @{dt} for hver periode hvor "
"aktivprisen var større end @{strike} (for en call) eller under den (for en "
"put)."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1332
msgid "OPT_SIMPLE_CHOOSER:theoretical price of a simple chooser option"
msgstr "OPT_SIMPLE_CHOOSER:Teoretisk pris på en simpel valgmuligheds option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1336
msgid "time1:time in years until the holder chooses a put or a call option"
msgstr "time1:tid i år indtil indehaveren vælger en put- eller call-option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1337
msgid "time2:time in years until the chosen option expires"
msgstr "time2:tid i år indtil den valgte option udløber"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1381
msgid "OPT_COMPLEX_CHOOSER:theoretical price of a complex chooser option"
msgstr "OPT_COMPLEX_CHOOSER:Teoretisk pris på en kompleks valgmuligheds option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1383
msgid "strike_call:strike price, if exercised as a call option"
msgstr "strike_call:strike-pris, hvis udnyttet som en call-option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1384
msgid "strike_put:strike price, if exercised as a put option"
msgstr "strike_put:strike-pris, hvis udnyttet som en put-option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1385
msgid "time:time in years until the holder chooses a put or a call option"
msgstr "time:tid i år indtil indehaveren vælger en put- eller call-option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1386
msgid "time_call:time in years to maturity of the call option if chosen"
msgstr "time_call:tid i år til udløb af call-optionen hvis valgt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1387
msgid "time_put:time in years  to maturity of the put option if chosen"
msgstr "time_put:tid i år til udløb af put-optionen hvis valgt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1482
msgid "OPT_ON_OPTIONS:theoretical price of options on options"
msgstr "OPT_ON_OPTIONS:Teoretisk pris på optioner på optioner"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1483
msgid ""
"type_flag:'cc' for calls on calls, 'cp' for calls on puts, and so on for "
"'pc', and 'pp'"
msgstr ""
"type_flag:'cc' for calls på calls, 'cp' for calls på puts, og så videre for "
"'pc' og 'pp'"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1485
msgid "strike1:strike price at which the option being valued is struck"
msgstr "strike1:strike-pris hvorved den værdiansatte option udnyttes"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1486
msgid "strike2:strike price at which the underlying option is struck"
msgstr "strike2:strike-pris hvorved den underliggende option udnyttes"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1487
msgid "time1:time in years to maturity of the option"
msgstr "time1:tid i år til optionens udløb"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1488
msgid "time2:time in years to the maturity of the underlying option"
msgstr "time2:tid i år til den underliggende options udløb"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1490
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry:net cost of holding the underlying asset of the underlying "
"option"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry:nettoomkostning ved at besidde det underliggende aktiv for den "
"underliggende option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1491
msgid ""
"volatility:annualized volatility in price of the underlying asset of the "
"underlying option"
msgstr ""
"volatility:årlig volatilitet i prisen på det underliggende aktiv for den "
"underliggende option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1492
msgid ""
"For common stocks, @{cost_of_carry} is the risk free rate less the dividend "
"yield."
msgstr ""
"For almindelige aktier er @{cost_of_carry} den risikofrie rente minus "
"udbytteudbyttet."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1493
msgid "@{time2} ≥ @{time1}"
msgstr "@{time2} ≥ @{time1}"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1559
msgid "OPT_EXTENDIBLE_WRITER:theoretical price of extendible writer options"
msgstr "OPT_EXTENDIBLE_WRITER:Teoretisk pris på forlængelige salgsoptioner"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1562
msgid "strike1:strike price at which the option is struck"
msgstr "strike1:strike-pris hvorved optionen udnyttes"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1563
msgid ""
"strike2:strike price at which the option is re-struck if out of the money at "
"@{time1}"
msgstr ""
"strike2:strike-pris til hvilken optionen gensættes hvis den er uden for "
"pengene ved @{time1}"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1564
msgid "time1:initial maturity of the option in years"
msgstr "time1:oprindelig udløbstid for optionen i år"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1565
msgid "time2:extended maturity in years if chosen"
msgstr "time2:forlænget udløbstid i år hvis valgt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1569
msgid ""
"OPT_EXTENDIBLE_WRITER models the theoretical price of extendible writer "
"options. These are options that have their maturity extended to @{time2} if "
"the option is out of the money at @{time1}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_EXTENDIBLE_WRITER modellerer den teoretiske pris for forlængelige "
"udsteder-optioner. Dette er optioner der får deres løbetid forlænget til "
"@{time2} hvis optionen er uden for pengene ved @{time1}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1611
msgid ""
"OPT_2_ASSET_CORRELATION:theoretical price of options on 2 assets with "
"correlation @{rho}"
msgstr ""
"OPT_2_ASSET_CORRELATION:Teoretisk pris for optioner på 2 aktiver med "
"korrelation @{rho}"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1613
msgid "spot1:spot price of the underlying asset of the first option"
msgstr "spot1:spotpris for det underliggende aktiv for den første option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1614
msgid "spot2:spot price of the underlying asset of the second option"
msgstr "spot2:spotpris for det underliggende aktiv for den anden option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1615
msgid "strike1:strike prices of the first option"
msgstr "strike1:strike-priser for den første option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1616
msgid "strike2:strike prices of the second option"
msgstr "strike2:strike-priser for den anden option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1618
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry1:net cost of holding the underlying asset of the first option "
"(for common stocks, the risk free rate less the dividend yield)"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry1:nettoomkostning ved at besidde det underliggende aktiv for "
"den første option (for almindelige aktier, den risikofrie rente minus "
"udbytteudbyttet)"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1620
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry2:net cost of holding the underlying asset of the second option "
"(for common stocks, the risk free rate less the dividend yield)"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry2:nettoomkostning ved at besidde det underliggende aktiv for "
"den anden option (for almindelige aktier, den risikofrie rente minus "
"udbytteudbyttet)"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1623
msgid ""
"volatility1:annualized volatility in price of the underlying asset of the "
"first option"
msgstr ""
"volatility1:årlig volatilitet i prisen på det underliggende aktiv for den "
"første option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1624
msgid ""
"volatility2:annualized volatility in price of the underlying asset of the "
"second option"
msgstr ""
"volatility2:årlig volatilitet i prisen på det underliggende aktiv for den "
"anden option"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1625
msgid "rho:correlation between the two underlying assets"
msgstr "rho:korrelation mellem de to underliggende aktiver"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1626
msgid ""
"OPT_2_ASSET_CORRELATION models the theoretical price of options on 2 assets "
"with correlation @{rho}. The payoff for a call is max(@{spot2} - "
"@{strike2},0) if @{spot1} > @{strike1} or 0 otherwise. The payoff for a put "
"is max (@{strike2} - @{spot2}, 0) if @{spot1} < @{strike1} or 0 otherwise."
msgstr ""
"OPT_2_ASSET_CORRELATION modellerer den teoretiske pris for optioner på 2 "
"aktiver med korrelation @{rho}. Afkastet for en call er max(@{spot2} - "
"@{strike2},0) hvis @{spot1} > @{strike1} eller 0 ellers. Afkastet for en put "
"er max (@{strike2} - @{spot2}, 0) hvis @{spot1} < @{strike1} eller 0 ellers."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1661
msgid ""
"OPT_EURO_EXCHANGE:theoretical price of a European option to exchange assets"
msgstr ""
"OPT_EURO_EXCHANGE:Teoretisk pris på en europæisk option til at bytte aktiver"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1662
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1706
msgid "spot1:spot price of asset 1"
msgstr "spot1:spotpris for aktiv 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1663
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1707
msgid "spot2:spot price of asset 2"
msgstr "spot2:spotpris for aktiv 2"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1664
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1708
msgid "qty1:quantity of asset 1"
msgstr "qty1:mængde af aktiv 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1665
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1709
msgid "qty2:quantity of asset 2"
msgstr "qty2:mængde af aktiv 2"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1668
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1712
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry1:net cost of holding asset 1 (for common stocks, the risk free "
"rate less the dividend yield)"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry1:nettoomkostning ved at besidde aktiv 1 (for almindelige "
"aktier, den risikofrie rente minus udbytteudbyttet)"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1670
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1714
msgid ""
"cost_of_carry2:net cost of holding asset 2 (for common stocks, the risk free "
"rate less the dividend yield)"
msgstr ""
"cost_of_carry2:nettoomkostning ved at besidde aktiv 2 (for almindelige "
"aktier, den risikofrie rente minus udbytteudbyttet)"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1672
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1716
msgid "volatility1:annualized volatility in price of asset 1"
msgstr "volatility1:årlig volatilitet i prisen for aktiv 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1673
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1717
msgid "volatility2:annualized volatility in price of asset 2"
msgstr "volatility2:årlig volatilitet i prisen for aktiv 2"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1674
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1718
msgid "rho:correlation between the prices of the two assets"
msgstr "rho:korrelation mellem priserne på de to aktiver"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1675
msgid ""
"OPT_EURO_EXCHANGE models the theoretical price of a European option to "
"exchange one asset with quantity @{qty2} and spot price @{spot2} for another "
"with quantity @{qty1} and spot price @{spot1}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_EURO_EXCHANGE modellerer den teoretiske pris for en europæisk option til "
"at bytte ét aktiv med mængde @{qty2} og spotpris @{spot2} til et andet med "
"mængde @{qty1} og spotpris @{spot1}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1705
msgid ""
"OPT_AMER_EXCHANGE:theoretical price of an American option to exchange assets"
msgstr ""
"OPT_AMER_EXCHANGE:Teoretisk pris på en amerikansk option til at bytte aktiver"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1719
msgid ""
"OPT_AMER_EXCHANGE models the theoretical price of an American option to "
"exchange one asset with quantity @{qty2} and spot price @{spot2} for another "
"with quantity @{qty1} and spot price @{spot1}."
msgstr ""
"OPT_AMER_EXCHANGE modellerer den teoretiske pris for en amerikansk option "
"til at bytte ét aktiv med mængde @{qty2} og spotpris @{spot2} til et andet "
"med mængde @{qty1} og spotpris @{spot1}."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1749
msgid ""
"OPT_SPREAD_APPROX:theoretical price of a European option on the spread "
"between two futures contracts"
msgstr ""
"OPT_SPREAD_APPROX:Teoretisk pris på en europæisk option på spændet mellem to "
"futureskontrakter"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1751
msgid "fut_price1:price of the first futures contract"
msgstr "fut_price1:pris for den første futureskontrakt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1752
msgid "fut_price2:price of the second futures contract"
msgstr "fut_price2:pris for den anden futureskontrakt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1756
msgid ""
"volatility1:annualized volatility in price of the first underlying futures "
"contract"
msgstr ""
"volatility1:årlig volatilitet i prisen på den første underliggende "
"futureskontrakt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1757
msgid ""
"volatility2:annualized volatility in price of the second underlying futures "
"contract"
msgstr ""
"volatility2:årlig volatilitet i prisen på den anden underliggende "
"futureskontrakt"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1758
msgid "rho:correlation between the two futures contracts"
msgstr "rho:korrelation mellem de to futureskontrakter"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1804
msgid ""
"OPT_FLOAT_STRK_LKBK:theoretical price of floating-strike lookback option"
msgstr ""
"OPT_FLOAT_STRK_LKBK:Teoretisk pris på tilbagebliksoption med flydende strike"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1807
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1871
msgid "spot_min:minimum spot price of the underlying asset so far observed"
msgstr ""
"spot_min:mindste spotpris for det underliggende aktiv observeret hidtil"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1808
#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1872
msgid "spot_max:maximum spot price of the underlying asset so far observed"
msgstr ""
"spot_max:højeste spotpris for det underliggende aktiv observeret hidtil"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1813
msgid ""
"OPT_FLOAT_STRK_LKBK determines the theoretical price of a floating-strike "
"lookback option where the holder of the option may exercise on expiry at the "
"most favourable price observed during the options life of the underlying "
"asset."
msgstr ""
"OPT_FLOAT_STRK_LKBK bestemmer den teoretiske pris for en floating-strike "
"lookback-option hvor indehaveren af optionen kan udnytte ved udløb til den "
"mest fordelagtige pris observeret i løbet af optionens levetid for det "
"underliggende aktiv."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1868
msgid "OPT_FIXED_STRK_LKBK:theoretical price of a fixed-strike lookback option"
msgstr ""
"OPT_FIXED_STRK_LKBK:Teoretisk pris på tilbagebliksoption med fast strike"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1878
msgid ""
"OPT_FIXED_STRK_LKBK determines the theoretical price of a fixed-strike "
"lookback option where the holder of the option may exercise on expiry at the "
"most favourable price observed during the options life of the underlying "
"asset."
msgstr ""
"OPT_FIXED_STRK_LKBK bestemmer den teoretiske pris for en fixed-strike "
"lookback-option hvor indehaveren af optionen kan udnytte ved udløb til den "
"mest fordelagtige pris observeret i løbet af optionens levetid for det "
"underliggende aktiv."

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1952
msgid ""
"OPT_BINOMIAL:theoretical price of either an American or European style "
"option using a binomial tree"
msgstr ""
"OPT_BINOMIAL:Teoretisk pris på enten en amerikansk eller europæisk option "
"ved brug af et binomialtræ"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1953
msgid ""
"amer_euro_flag:'a' for an American style option or 'e' for a European style "
"option"
msgstr ""
"amer_euro_flag:'a' for en option i amerikansk stil eller 'e' for en option i "
"europæisk stil"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1955
msgid "num_time_steps:number of time steps used in the valuation"
msgstr "num_time_steps:antal tidstrin brugt i værdiansættelsen"

#: ../plugins/fn-derivatives/options.c:1962
msgid ""
"A larger @{num_time_steps} yields greater accuracy but  OPT_BINOMIAL is "
"slower to calculate."
msgstr ""
"En større @{num_time_steps} giver større nøjagtighed men OPT_BINOMIAL er "
"langsommere at beregne."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:214
msgid "BASE:string of digits representing the number @{n} in base @{b}"
msgstr ""
"BASE:Tegnstreng af cifre der repræsenterer tallet @{n} med grundtal @{b}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:215 ../plugins/fn-numtheory/numtheory.c:822
#: ../plugins/fn-numtheory/numtheory.c:853
msgid "n:integer"
msgstr "n:heltal"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:216
msgid "b:base (2 ≤ @{b} ≤ 36)"
msgstr "b:grundtal (2 ≤ @{b} ≤ 36)"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:217
msgid "length:minimum length of the resulting string"
msgstr "length:minimumslængde for den resulterende streng"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:218
msgid ""
"BASE converts @{n} to its string representation in base @{b}. Leading zeroes "
"will be added to reach the minimum length given by @{length}."
msgstr ""
"BASE konverterer @{n} til dens strengrepræsentation i grundtal @{b}. "
"Foranstillede nuller vil blive tilføjet for at nå den minimumlængde givet "
"ved @{length}."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:244
msgid "BIN2DEC:decimal representation of the binary number @{x}"
msgstr "BIN2DEC:Decimalrepræsentation af det binære tal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:245 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:267
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:291
msgid ""
"x:a binary number, either as a string or as a number involving only the "
"digits 0 and 1"
msgstr ""
"x:et binært tal, enten som en streng eller som et tal der kun involverer "
"cifrene 0 og 1"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:266
msgid "BIN2OCT:octal representation of the binary number @{x}"
msgstr "BIN2OCT:Oktal repræsentation af det binære tal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:268 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:292
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:317 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:347
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:370 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:448
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:471 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:494
#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:517
msgid "places:number of digits"
msgstr "places:antal cifre"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:269
msgid ""
"If @{places} is given, BIN2OCT pads the result with zeros to achieve exactly "
"@{places} digits. If this is not possible, BIN2OCT returns #NUM!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{places} er givet, fylder BIN2OCT resultatet med nuller for at opnå "
"præcis @{places} cifre. Hvis dette ikke er muligt, returnerer BIN2OCT #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:290
msgid "BIN2HEX:hexadecimal representation of the binary number @{x}"
msgstr "BIN2HEX:Heksadecimal repræsentation af det binære tal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:293
msgid ""
"If @{places} is given, BIN2HEX pads the result with zeros to achieve exactly "
"@{places} digits. If this is not possible, BIN2HEX returns #NUM!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{places} er givet, fylder BIN2HEX resultatet med nuller for at opnå "
"præcis @{places} cifre. Hvis dette ikke er muligt, returnerer BIN2HEX #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:315
msgid "DEC2BIN:binary representation of the decimal number @{x}"
msgstr "DEC2BIN:Binær repræsentation af decimaltal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:316
msgid "x:integer (− 513 < @{x} < 512)"
msgstr "x:heltal (− 513 < @{x} < 512)"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:318
msgid ""
"If @{places} is given and @{x} is non-negative, DEC2BIN pads the result with "
"zeros to achieve exactly @{places} digits. If this is not possible, DEC2BIN "
"returns #NUM!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{places} er givet og @{x} er ikke-negativ, fylder DEC2BIN resultatet "
"med nuller for at opnå præcis @{places} cifre. Hvis dette ikke er muligt, "
"returnerer DEC2BIN #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:322
msgid "If @{places} is given and @{x} is negative, @{places} is ignored."
msgstr "Hvis @{places} er givet og @{x} er negativ, så ignoreres @{places}."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:323
msgid "If @{x} < − 512 or @{x} > 511, DEC2BIN returns #NUM!"
msgstr "Hvis @{x} < − 512 eller @{x} > 511, så returnerer DEC2BIN #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:345
msgid "DEC2OCT:octal representation of the decimal number @{x}"
msgstr "DEC2OCT:Oktal repræsentation af decimaltal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:346 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:369
msgid "x:integer"
msgstr "x:heltal"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:348
msgid ""
"If @{places} is given, DEC2OCT pads the result with zeros to achieve exactly "
"@{places} digits. If this is not possible, DEC2OCT returns #NUM!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{places} er givet, fylder DEC2OCT resultatet med nuller for at opnå "
"præcis @{places} cifre. Hvis dette ikke er muligt, returnerer DEC2OCT #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:368
msgid "DEC2HEX:hexadecimal representation of the decimal number @{x}"
msgstr "DEC2HEX:Heksadecimal repræsentation af decimaltal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:371
msgid ""
"If @{places} is given, DEC2HEX pads the result with zeros to achieve exactly "
"@{places} digits. If this is not possible, DEC2HEX returns #NUM!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis @{places} er givet, fylder DEC2HEX resultatet med nuller for at opnå "
"præcis @{places} cifre. Hvis dette ikke er muligt, returnerer DEC2HEX #TAL!"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:391
msgid "DECIMAL:decimal representation of @{x}"
msgstr "DECIMAL:Decimalrepræsentation af @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:392
msgid "x:number in base @{base}"
msgstr "x:tal i grundtal @{base}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:393
msgid "base:base of @{x}, (2 ≤ @{base} ≤ 36)"
msgstr "base:grundtal for @{x}, (2 ≤ @{base} ≤ 36)"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:422
msgid "OCT2DEC:decimal representation of the octal number @{x}"
msgstr "OCT2DEC:Decimalrepræsentation af det oktale tal @{x}"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:423 ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:447
