msgid "HEXREP returns a hexadecimal string representation of @{x}."
msgstr "HEXREP returnerer en heksadecimal strengrepræsentation af @{x}."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1527
msgid ""
"This is a function meant for debugging.  The layout of the result may change "
"and even depend on how Gnumeric was compiled."
msgstr ""
"Dette er en funktion beregnet til fejlfinding. Layoutet af resultatet kan "
"ændre sig og endda afhænge af hvordan Gnumeric blev kompileret."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1556
msgid "INVSUMINV:the reciprocal of the sum of reciprocals of the arguments"
msgstr ""
"INVSUMINV:Den reciprokke værdi af summen af reciprokke værdier af "
"argumenterne"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1557
msgid "x0:non-negative number"
msgstr "x0:ikke-negativt tal"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1558
msgid "x1:non-negative number"
msgstr "x1:ikke-negativt tal"

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1559
msgid ""
"If any of the arguments is negative, #VALUE! is returned.\n"
"If any argument is zero, the result is zero."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et af argumenterne er negativt, så returneres fejlen #VÆRDI!\n"
"Hvis et af argumenterne er nul, er resultatet nul."

#: ../plugins/fn-eng/functions.c:1561
msgid ""
"INVSUMINV sum calculates the reciprocal (the inverse) of the sum of "
"reciprocals (inverses) of all its arguments."
msgstr ""
"INVSUMINV sum beregner den reciprokke (inverse) af summen af reciprokke "
