msgid "actual_range:observed data"
msgstr "actual_range:observerede data"

#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:1200
msgid "theoretical_range:expected values"
msgstr "theoretical_range:forventede værdier"

#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:1201
msgid ""
"If the actual range is not an n by 1 or 1 by n range, but an n by m range, "
"then CHITEST uses (n-1) times (m-1) as degrees of freedom. This is useful if "
"the expected values were calculated from the observed value in a test of "
"independence or test of homogeneity."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det faktiske interval ikke er et n×1 eller 1×n interval, men et n×m "
"interval, så bruger CHITEST (n-1) gange (m-1) som frihedsgrader. Dette er "
"nyttigt hvis de forventede værdier blev beregnet fra den observerede værdi i "
"en uafhængighedstest eller homogenitetstest."

#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:1207
msgid "CHITEST is the OpenFormula function LEGACY.CHITEST."
msgstr "CHITEST er OpenFormula-funktionen LEGACY.CHITEST."

#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:1285
