"If there are less than 5 or more than 5000 sample values, SFTEST returns "
"#VALUE!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er færre end fem eller mere end 5000 eksempelværdier, så returnerer "
"SFTEST #VALUE!"

#: ../plugins/fn-stat/functions.c:5292
msgid "CVMTEST:Cramér-von Mises Test of Normality"
msgstr "CVMTEST:Cramér-von Mises-test for normalitet"

