"CP1252 (Windows-1252) is also known as the \"ANSI code page\", but it is not "
"an ANSI standard."
msgstr ""
"CP1252 (Windows-1252) er også kendt som \"ANSI-kodesiden\", men det er ikke "
"en ANSI-standard."

