msgid ""
"CP1252 (Windows-1252) is based on an early draft of ISO-8859-1, and contains "
"all of its printable characters. It also contains all of ISO-8859-15's "
"printable characters (but partially at different positions.)"
msgstr ""
"CP1252 (Windows-1252) er baseret på et tidligt udkast af ISO-8859-1 og "
"indeholder alle dets udskrivbare tegn. Den indeholder også alle "
"ISO-8859-15's udskrivbare tegn (men delvist på forskellige positioner.)"

#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:64 ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:165
msgid ""
"In CP1252 (Windows-1252), 129, 141, 143, 144, and 157 do not have matching "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"I CP1252 (Windows-1252) har 129, 141, 143, 144 og 157 ikke matchende tegn."

#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:65 ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:166
msgid ""
"For @{x} from 1 to 255 except 129, 141, 143, 144, and 157 we have "
"CODE(CHAR(@{x}))=@{x}."
msgstr ""
"For @{x} fra 1 til 255 undtagen 129, 141, 143, 144 og 157 har vi "
"CODE(CHAR(@{x}))=@{x}."

