msgstr "@{c} skal være et gyldigt CP1252-tegn (Windows-1252)."

#: ../plugins/fn-string/functions.c:164
msgid ""
"CP1252 (Windows-1252) is based on an early draft of ISO-8859-1, and contains "
"all of its printable characters (but partially at different positions.)"
msgstr ""
"CP1252 (Windows-1252) er baseret på et tidligt udkast af ISO-8859-1 og "
